 created</item></change><change n="meta.1730"><date>16.08.2008</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.1730"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>257BC</date>
<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀλέξανδρος Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαί τε καὶ ἐν τοῖς λοιποῖς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κατὰ νοῦν</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="editorial"><lem>ἀπαλλάσσεις</lem><rdg>απαλλασεις</rdg></app>, εἴη ἂν ὡς ἡμεῖς βουλόμεθα. ἐρρώμεθα δὲ καὶ αὐτοί. παραγ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ινομένου</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸς ὑμᾶς Μυὸς ἔδοξεν ἡμῖν βέλτιον εἶναι αὐτῶι τε τῶι Μυὶ ὑπόμνημα <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ποστεῖλαι ἐν ὧι</supplied> 

    <lb n="4"/>μνησθῆι Ἀπολλωνίωι περὶ τῆς συντάξεως ἧς ἔταξεν <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημιμ</sic></choice> Μένετ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ος. ὑ</supplied>πὸ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ούτου δ᾽</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οὐδὲ</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>πο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αχθῆναι ἕως</supplied></rdg></app> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὴν</supplied> 

    <lb n="5"/>ὀφειλομένην κεκο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>ίσμεθα <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ὔτε ἀφ᾽ οὗ χρόνου <choice><corr>ἐκεῖνος</corr><sic>κεινος</sic></choice> τετελεύτηκε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν οὐδεὶς</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied cert="low" reason="lost">ἡμῖν</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὴν σύνταξιν</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="6"/>ἀποδίδωσιν. καλῶς δ᾽ ἔχειν ὑπέλαβον καί σοι γράψαι ὅπως ἐάν τινά σου χρεί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αν τὰ πράγμα</supplied>-

    <lb n="7"/><app type="editorial"><lem>τα</lem><rdg><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">παρόν</supplied>τα</rdg></app> ἔχηι συναντιλάβηι φιλοτίμως καὶ ἡμῶν ἕνεκεν καὶ Μενέτου. οἷα ἂν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἰτήσωμέν σου</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>βουληθέντος πάντα ἡμῖν τὰ φιλάνθρωπα ἔσται παρ᾽ Ἀπολλωνίου, καὶ ἡμεῖς <app type="editorial"><lem><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υνησόμεθα</supplied></lem><rdg><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιαγνωσόμεθα</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="9"/>διὰ σὲ <choice><corr>σεσῷσθαι</corr><sic>σεσωισθαι</sic></choice> καὶ ἀνεστάναι. περὶ ὧν σπουδάσομεν καὶ αὐτοὶ κα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear>᾽ ὅσο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἡμῖ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> κ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αὶ δυνατὸν</supplied> 

    <lb n="10"/>τὰς χάριτας ἀποδιδόναι σοι. 

    <lb n="11"/><space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="12"/><handShift new="m2"/> Ἀλέξανδρος περὶ τῆς γινομένης 

    <lb n="13"/>αὐτῶι συντάξεως. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="28">κη</num> Δύστρου <num value="24">κδ</num>. 

    <lb n="14"/><choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> Μέμφει. 

    <lb n="12"/>Ζήνωνι </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0257-04-27" type="textDate">vor 27. Apr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 13: <date type="mentioned" value="-0257-04-27">27. Apr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Col.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">9</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1730</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0094</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">9</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0094;3;9" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">88</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">nach S. 44</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">White, Ancient Letters (1986), 13</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div><div n="meta.1730" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://wwwapp.cc.columbia.edu/ldpd/app/apis/item?mode=item&amp;key=columbia.apis.p9"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>